shag = 1.2 dim priv[3] dim coord_s[][5] priv[ix] = 0 priv[iy] = 0 priv[iz] = 0 n_otr = vardim1(otr) n_c = 0 for i = 1 to n_otr r = otr[i][7] phi = otr[i][8] etta = otr[i][9] n_int = round_int(r / shag) delta = r - n_int * shag addr = 0 if delta > EPS then addr = delta/2 for jj = 1 to n_int n_c = n_c + 1 coord_s[n_c][ix] = otr[i][ix+3] + addr * sin(etta+90) * cos(phi) coord_s[n_c][iy] = otr[i][iy+3] + addr * sin(etta+90) * sin(phi) coord_s[n_c][iz] = otr[i][iz+3] + addr * cos(etta+90) coord_s[n_c][4] = phi coord_s[n_c][5] = etta text2 coord_s[n_c][ix], coord_s[n_c][iy], addr addr = addr + shag next jj next i
